1
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,799
You've moved on.

2
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:45,359
But I haven't.

3
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:46,760
Cao Ping.

4
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,040
Look ahead.

5
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,400
Stop clinging to the past.

6
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:55,519
From the day I went to prison,

7
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:57,760
I did try to look ahead.

8
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,040
For the past two years,

9
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,599
every day, I worked to turn myself around.

10
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,239
So I could get out sooner

11
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:04,159
and reunite with my sister.

12
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,120
What exactly do you want?

13
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:15,759
I don't want anything.

14
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,840
I just want to tell you,

15
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,360
don't touch my sister.

16
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,199
Or I won't let

17
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:22,520
the people around you live in peace.

18
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:30,120
I never touched your sister.

19
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,280
Our grudge

20
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:33,919
is between us.

21
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,599
Come at me if you've got guts.

22
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:39,599
Stop fighting.

23
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,479
Keep this up and I'll call the police.

24
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:42,960
Xing Wu.

25
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,000
Xing Wu.

26
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,680
We're not done.

27
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,879
Who is he?

28
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:01,199
Someone I know.

29
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:04,120
Why did you two fight?

30
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,560
It's nothing.

31
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,680
You almost fought.

32
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,719
How is that nothing?

33
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,400
Before you came to Zhazhating,

34
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,840
I got into fights

35
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,520
more times than I can count.

36
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:17,280
Xing Wu.

37
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:18,919
Xing Wu.

38
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,360
If anything happens,

39
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,639
you have to tell me.

40
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:58,280
Our grudge

41
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,719
is between us.

42
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,439
Come at me if you've got guts.

43
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,520
Don't touch my family.

44
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,919
That'd be too easy on you.

45
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,759
Xing Wu.

46
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,639
As long as I'm alive,

47
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,960
I won't let you have it easy.

48
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,520
I'll drag your life
down into the same

49
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,319
gutter as mine.

50
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,279
Thanks.
I'll do it, Auntie.

51
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:25,839
Okay.

52
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,319
I transferred the money to you.

53
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,439
Let's go buy some meat.

54
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:33,160
What else do you want?

55
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,319
Anything is fine.

56
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:35,600
Li, come here.

57
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:36,319
Fresh tenderloin.
Want a piece?

58
00:04:36,879 --> 00:04:37,759
Fresh like fresh?

59
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:39,839
I'll take this one.
Sure.

60
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:41,519
And two pig's trotters.

61
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,680
Sure, no problem.

62
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:43,720
Here you go.

63
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,759
Okay. I got it.
Come again.

64
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,600
Grandma said

65
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,920
you and Wu have been studying

66
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,639
so hard lately,

67
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:52,439
so you need good nutrition.

68
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:53,959
Ye.

69
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,439
Why are you so distracted?

70
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:58,920
It's nothing.

71
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:01,839
Is it Xing Wu?

72
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,240
I just feel like

73
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,959
he's always carrying something inside.

74
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,399
Did you two have a fight?

75
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:13,000
No.

76
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,279
I just don't quite understand him.

77
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:18,519
Auntie.

78
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:20,079
He's like a clam.

79
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,560
You know something's
locked up inside,

80
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,279
but you can't get him to open up.

81
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,079
Do you ever feel that way?

82
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,319
Yes.

83
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,639
Of course I do.

84
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,319
When Wu was little,

85
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,839
I did have the energy to look after him.

86
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,759
I always wanted to know

87
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:36,000
what was really on his mind,

88
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:36,839
afraid that something

89
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:37,959
was upsetting him

90
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:39,040
and he'd keep it all bottled up.

91
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:40,519
When I was young,

92
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,920
I wanted to be a good mother too.

93
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,800
And then?

94
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:46,240
Then I couldn't even

95
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,279
take care of myself.

96
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:49,399
Every day I had debts to pay,

97
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:51,279
food to put on the table.

98
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:52,680
How could I watch him?

99
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,360
But Wu
was a pretty sensible kid.

100
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,879
They say the child who cries

101
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,800
gets the milk.

102
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:59,639
But he never cried.

103
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:01,800
He never asked me for anything either.

104
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:04,399
After a while, I just treated it

105
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,560
as if nothing had happened,

106
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,399
as if everything was fine.

107
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,959
I got used to it.

108
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:09,759
I stopped worrying.

109
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,160
Let's go.

110
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:13,680
Let's buy some yam too.

111
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,839
Pig's trotters stewed with yam.

112
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,920
Wu's favorite.

113
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,199
Your grades lately

114
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,040
are like a roller coaster.

115
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,519
You dropped nearly a hundred points.

116
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,199
On the next exam,

117
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,720
you'd better work harder.

118
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,519
Don't worry. I know.

119
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:40,920
Cousin.
Bro Wu.

120
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,560
Weren't you riding bikes?

121
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,879
Why are you on the bus too?

122
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:47,959
The wheel broke.

123
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:52,279
It's been windy lately.

124
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:53,199
Too lazy to ride.

125
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,920
And I can squeeze in some vocab.

126
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:58,600
Not bad.

127
00:06:58,879 --> 00:07:00,160
You finally know how to study.

128
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:01,519
Xing Wu.

129
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,560
You're losing.

130
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:03,759
I won't.

131
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,639
I won't.

132
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,000
What's this?

133
00:07:10,759 --> 00:07:11,680
Testing whether phone location
still works.

134
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,120
Why not just call?

135
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,639
What if it's urgent?

136
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,199
Three quick taps. Way easier.

137
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:26,199
Let's go.

138
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,279
Wenhui, did you hear?

139
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,319
Cao Fan's brother

140
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:39,439
served two years for stabbing someone.

141
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,879
Really?

142
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:42,000
Don't believe rumors.

143
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,079
Of course it's fake.

144
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,519
Cao Fan's family

145
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,399
is pretty well-off, isn't it?

146
00:07:45,439 --> 00:07:46,639
She always ranks top three too.

147
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,040
Use your brain.

148
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:49,480
If there were nothing to it,

149
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,519
would everyone be talking?

150
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,879
Then it must be true.

151
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,959
They say it with so much detail.

152
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:57,120
They even say it has to do with Xing Wu.

153
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:57,959
What do you mean?

154
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,800
I saw Cao Fan this weekend.

155
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:01,079
She was at some

156
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:03,279
rundown laundry shop cleaning shoes.

157
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:04,959
I went up and asked her.

158
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:06,160
She looked so guilty.

159
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,279
She even said her brother

160
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:08,519
was a boss in Shenzhen.

161
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:09,399
To me,

162
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,800
her brother is just an ex-con.

163
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,560
No wonder her clothes

164
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,040
smell like a laundry shop.

165
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:15,000
And she said

166
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,040
her clothes

167
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,199
were sent to a laundry shop

168
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,160
to be cleaned.

169
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,720
Who's she playing, some rich princess?

170
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,959
If she weren't good at school

171
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,000
and we couldn't copy her homework,

172
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:29,319
who'd want to hang out with her?

173
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,080
Having a little gossip party?

174
00:08:34,279 --> 00:08:35,320
Why are you everywhere?

175
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,559
You heard everything we said?

176
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,639
From which part?

177
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,519
From Cao Fan's brother,

178
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:41,960
or Cao Fan?

179
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:44,440
You were talking so loudly.

180
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:45,399
Why not use a megaphone

181
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:46,759
so the whole school can hear?

182
00:08:47,399 --> 00:08:48,720
So what if you heard?

183
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,639
About your dad,

184
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:50,679
she was the one who spread it.

185
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,360
I'm kind of getting back at her for you.

186
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,559
No need.

187
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:55,600
Back then, those rumors

188
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,080
you helped spread too.

189
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,159
Don't make it sound like

190
00:08:58,159 --> 00:08:59,360
you defended me.

191
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,720
Let me give you both a friendly warning.

192
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:06,440
You may be close now,

193
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,519
but who knows what happens later?

194
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,360
You heard all that, right?

195
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,720
Now I'm everyone's target.

196
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:22,720
You must be thrilled.

197
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:23,960
I'm not thrilled.

198
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,200
I never think

199
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,519
attacking someone over family matters

200
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:27,320
is anything to be proud of.

201
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,519
Every family has ups and downs.

202
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:30,720
We're students.

203
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,039
We should just focus on studying.

204
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,159
No one wants

205
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:35,360
to be pushed into the spotlight,

206
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,320
right?

207
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,759
Mind your own business.

208
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,200
No one asked you to stand up for me.

209
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,279
I'm standing up

210
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:43,120
for what's right.

211
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,720
Not for you.

212
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,639
Your nose is bleeding.

213
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,240
Here. Tissue.

214
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,279
Don't pretend to care about me.

215
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,080
We're not close.

216
00:09:59,200 --> 00:09:59,679
And

217
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,360
you'd better not tell anyone

218
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,519
about Xing Wu and my brother.

219
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:03,799
Their grudge

220
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,919
has nothing to do with me.

221
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:06,519
I owe you one this time.

222
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:08,519
Grudge?

223
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,720
There was a boy in the same game.

224
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,600
He didn't like him,

225
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:18,960
so they had a conflict.

226
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:21,720
He slashed his back with a knife.

227
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,120
Cao Fan's brother

228
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:25,600
served two years for stabbing someone.

229
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:26,720
If there were nothing to it,

230
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,600
would everyone be talking?

231
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,080
Then it must be true.

232
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:31,519
They even say it has to do with Xing Wu.

233
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,200
One camera at the entrance

234
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:37,919
should be enough.

235
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,000
No need inside, right?

236
00:10:40,519 --> 00:10:41,879
The brand you bought

237
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:42,759
isn't cheap either.
Nail.

238
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:44,440
It's expensive.

239
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,320
Better safe than sorry.

240
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,000
Yang Gang has Cao Ping backing him now.

241
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:49,240
Those guys
will probably come

242
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,879
to cause trouble from time to time.

243
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,600
Last time, so many of them came,

244
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,159
and nothing serious happened, right?

245
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:55,840
Don't be too nervous.

246
00:10:56,559 --> 00:10:57,320
What if one day
I can't get here in time?

247
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,399
If things get out of hand,

248
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,120
another camera means more protection.

249
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,519
It can be evidence if we call the police.

250
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,879
I'm fine.

251
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,159
Cao Ping must be after you.

252
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:08,320
If you need help,

253
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:09,399
you must tell us.

254
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:10,639
Dahei and I

255
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:11,919
are ready to charge in with you anytime.

256
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,519
Charge in? Charge into what?

257
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:20,000
Watched too many gangster movies?

258
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:22,200
If your sister knew I took you fighting,

259
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,840
she'll destroy us both.

260
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:25,840
True.

261
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:28,120
Sometimes,

262
00:11:28,399 --> 00:11:29,840
fists don't solve problems.

263
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,200
If Cao Ping

264
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,200
keeps coming after you,

265
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,600
what are you going to do?

266
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:41,159
Stop worrying.

267
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:46,600
Dahei.

268
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:48,240
Bro Wu.
What is it?

269
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:51,320
I need to prepare for the exam lately.

270
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,200
I probably

271
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:53,799
won't have much time to come to Shunyi.

272
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,600
I don't feel easy leaving Quanya alone.

273
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:56,840
If you're free,

274
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,080
help me keep an eye on things.

275
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,720
Bro Wu, I know even if you don't say it.

276
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,440
Don't worry.

277
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,639
When the guys and I are free,
we'll go check on the place.

278
00:12:02,679 --> 00:12:03,759
You just focus on studying

279
00:12:03,799 --> 00:12:04,639
and prepare for the exam.

280
00:12:05,519 --> 00:12:05,960
Thanks.

281
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:08,200
We're brothers. No need to thank me.

282
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,840
We're all so jealous of you now.

283
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,399
Look at you in that school uniform.

284
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,120
You look proud.

285
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,679
People like us may spend

286
00:12:14,679 --> 00:12:15,559
our whole lives
stuck in this little shop.

287
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,519
But you're different, Bro Wu.

288
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:18,279
You're smart.

289
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,679
You have a mind for studying.

290
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,080
You finally went back to school.

291
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,159
You need to seize the chance.

292
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:23,080
Don't let the dirty mess
from the past

293
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:24,720
drag you down again.

294
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,519
Don't worry.
I know.

295
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,000
Good luck, Bro Wu.

296
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:33,399
I'm off.

297
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,000
Here, eat.

298
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:52,320
Why did you suddenly

299
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,360
treat us to skewers?

300
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:54,440
I want to ask you something.

301
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,000
What is it?

302
00:12:59,919 --> 00:13:00,679
At school,

303
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,320
people have been saying

304
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:03,720
that

305
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:06,759
Cao Fan's brother did two years in prison

306
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:07,759
and just got out.

307
00:13:08,639 --> 00:13:09,720
Have you heard that?

308
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,919
Xing Wu's enemy

309
00:13:16,519 --> 00:13:17,679
is Cao Fan's brother, right?

310
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,720
I don't know.

311
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:21,799
There are rumors
even I don't know?

312
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,120
Then it must be a rumor.

313
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,120
Right.

314
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:27,720
The scar on Xing Wu's back

315
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,600
was from him two years ago.

316
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,759
That's why he served two years.

317
00:13:33,399 --> 00:13:34,519
He only got out recently.

318
00:13:35,279 --> 00:13:35,759
Right?

319
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,120
Undercooked.

320
00:13:41,399 --> 00:13:42,759
Xing Wu was afraid he'd go after me,

321
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:43,759
and so he asked
you two to follow me.

322
00:13:45,639 --> 00:13:46,519
Am I wrong?

323
00:13:47,039 --> 00:13:47,799
The skewers need sauce.

324
00:13:47,799 --> 00:13:49,039
I'll go get some.

325
00:13:49,159 --> 00:13:50,840
Feels like not enough skewers.

326
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,559
I'll grab more.

327
00:13:55,399 --> 00:13:57,320
You two are terrible actors.

328
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,279
Your faces tell me

329
00:14:00,279 --> 00:14:01,000
I guessed right.

330
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,240
Sorry.

331
00:14:07,519 --> 00:14:08,759
The number you dialed

332
00:14:08,759 --> 00:14:10,039
is temporarily unavailable.

333
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,720
Sorry.

334
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:22,240
The number you dialed

335
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:26,799
Sorry.

336
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,399
The number you dialed

337
00:14:40,559 --> 00:14:41,240
Qing Ye figured out
your connection with Cao Ping.

338
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:42,519
Qing Ye?

339
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:43,799
She wouldn't let us follow her.

340
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,240
I'm afraid she may go find him.

341
00:14:45,279 --> 00:14:45,879
Qing Ye.

342
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:50,840
Qing Ye.

343
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:53,679
You...

344
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:55,840
Why are you panting?

345
00:15:56,559 --> 00:15:57,240
I'm sorry.

346
00:15:58,399 --> 00:15:59,320
Let me hold you for a while.

347
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,879
My phone died.

348
00:16:11,519 --> 00:16:12,879
Right before it shut off,

349
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:15,639
I saw you called me.

350
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:18,120
I quickly sent you my location.

351
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,240
I didn't expect

352
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:23,320
it would make you think I was in danger.

353
00:16:34,519 --> 00:16:35,519
As long as you're okay.

354
00:16:42,279 --> 00:16:43,120
Actually,

355
00:16:43,559 --> 00:16:45,080
after I sent you my location,

356
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,399
for one moment,

357
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:47,759
I thought

358
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:50,519
I might as well trick you,

359
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:52,559
let you fail to find me,

360
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,320
and let you feel

361
00:16:56,159 --> 00:16:57,600
what it's like to wait with no reply.

362
00:17:01,519 --> 00:17:02,720
But then I thought,

363
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:04,559
forget it.

364
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,000
No matter what,

365
00:17:09,039 --> 00:17:10,799
you have the right to keep secrets.

366
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:19,279
Then I'll tell you

367
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:21,720
what happened two years ago.

368
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,559
Two years ago,

369
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,599
Xuan Island was mortgaged by Xing Guodong.

370
00:17:32,519 --> 00:17:33,680
We were buried in debt.

371
00:17:34,079 --> 00:17:34,960
Grandma was in the hospital

372
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:36,839
and urgently needed money.

373
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:39,759
Back then, I decided

374
00:17:39,759 --> 00:17:41,039
to enter the city basketball tournament.

375
00:17:42,039 --> 00:17:43,240
If I won MVP,

376
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:44,960
there would be prize money.

377
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:52,839
Xuan Island, Xuan Island, we're the best!

378
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,240
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

379
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,839
Xing Wu! Xing Wu!

380
00:17:56,319 --> 00:17:57,559
Xing Wu! Xing Wu!

381
00:17:58,039 --> 00:17:59,240
Also in that tournament

382
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,599
was Cao Ping.

383
00:18:01,519 --> 00:18:01,880
At the time,

384
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:03,039
he was at another vocational school

385
00:18:03,279 --> 00:18:04,160
in his final year.

386
00:18:05,599 --> 00:18:06,440
For him,

387
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,720
winning that tournament

388
00:18:09,519 --> 00:18:10,519
was his last chance
to get into sports school.

389
00:18:13,119 --> 00:18:14,279
But he injured his Achilles tendon.

390
00:18:15,079 --> 00:18:16,519
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

391
00:18:16,559 --> 00:18:18,039
Jieba! Jieba!

392
00:18:18,119 --> 00:18:19,759
Jieba rules the court!

393
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,400
Jieba! Jieba!

394
00:18:21,559 --> 00:18:22,960
Brother Ping, how's your foot?

395
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:24,880
I'm fine.

396
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,240
We have to give it everything.
Do you hear me?

397
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,240
With Brother Ping's skills,

398
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,200
even injured,
winning MVP

399
00:18:30,039 --> 00:18:30,720
won't be a problem.
Right?

400
00:18:31,839 --> 00:18:32,920
We need everyone.

401
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:35,200
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

402
00:18:35,319 --> 00:18:36,640
Jieba! Jieba!

403
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:38,400
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

404
00:18:38,599 --> 00:18:40,240
Jieba! Jieba!

405
00:18:40,519 --> 00:18:41,839
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

406
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,680
We're the best!

407
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:45,599
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

408
00:19:02,319 --> 00:19:03,039
Go!

409
00:19:19,559 --> 00:19:20,079
Nice!

410
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,559
Xuan Island scores again.

411
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:22,519
That's Xing Wu.

412
00:19:22,559 --> 00:19:24,079
As a newcomer, he is unstoppable,

413
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,079
charging in fiercely.

414
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,720
He truly is a dark horse.

415
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:27,960
Cao Ping of Team Jieba

416
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:29,039
has finally met

417
00:19:29,039 --> 00:19:29,920
a strong opponent.

418
00:19:30,119 --> 00:19:30,720
Will today's
MVP title

419
00:19:31,519 --> 00:19:32,599
slip from his hands?

420
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:40,640
Go! Go! Go!

421
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:47,519
Go! Go! Go!

422
00:20:07,519 --> 00:20:17,000
Go! Go! Go!

423
00:20:19,359 --> 00:20:20,000
Are you okay?

424
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,960
Xing Wu.

425
00:20:44,119 --> 00:20:45,319
Let's congratulate Xing Wu

426
00:20:45,359 --> 00:20:46,359
on winning

427
00:20:46,359 --> 00:20:48,079
this tournament's MVP title.

428
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,799
Congratulations, Xuan Island.

429
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:53,519
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

430
00:20:53,599 --> 00:20:56,279
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

431
00:20:56,359 --> 00:20:59,039
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

432
00:20:59,079 --> 00:21:01,720
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

433
00:21:01,839 --> 00:21:05,319
Xuan Island! Xuan Island!

434
00:21:06,599 --> 00:21:07,359
Congrats, Bro Wu.

435
00:21:07,359 --> 00:21:08,880
You got MVP

436
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:09,799
and the prize money.

437
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,160
Xuan Island champions!

438
00:21:16,119 --> 00:21:18,039
Order whatever you want tonight.

439
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:18,880
Bro Wu's paying.

440
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:20,640
Really?

441
00:21:20,759 --> 00:21:22,279
When has Bro Wu ever lied to you?

442
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:23,519
Boss.

443
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:25,119
Twenty lamb kidneys.

444
00:21:25,279 --> 00:21:26,720
And twenty flank skewers.

445
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:28,039
Sure. Coming right up.

446
00:21:28,279 --> 00:21:29,559
Neither of you leaves tonight

447
00:21:29,799 --> 00:21:30,440
until you finish them.

448
00:21:30,519 --> 00:21:32,119
Boss, twenty meat skewers.

449
00:21:32,119 --> 00:21:32,960
And whatever else you recommend.

450
00:21:33,079 --> 00:21:34,559
Sure. One moment. Coming up.

451
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:36,200
Bro Wu.

452
00:21:36,599 --> 00:21:37,640
Cao Ping is here.

453
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,519
Look at his loser face.

454
00:21:42,519 --> 00:21:43,440
One look and you know he lost.

455
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:47,279
Congrats again, Bro Wu. Cheers.

456
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,000
Xing Wu.

457
00:21:54,079 --> 00:21:55,160
Congratulations on winning the game

458
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,039
and also taking today's
MVP.

459
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:00,079
I know your leg was injured.

460
00:22:01,039 --> 00:22:01,599
In this game,

461
00:22:01,599 --> 00:22:03,119
if your leg hadn't been hurt,

462
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,240
maybe MVP would've been yours.

463
00:22:06,119 --> 00:22:07,599
You didn't just win prize money today.

464
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:10,039
I heard a provincial team coach

465
00:22:10,319 --> 00:22:11,160
wants you on the team.

466
00:22:11,519 --> 00:22:13,079
I'm not interested in the provincial team.

467
00:22:14,119 --> 00:22:15,119
I don't want to be an athlete.

468
00:22:15,519 --> 00:22:17,240
I just needed the prize money.

469
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,400
What are you pretending for?

470
00:22:18,759 --> 00:22:19,519
Can you stand up
when you talk to Ping?

471
00:22:20,839 --> 00:22:21,880
Did you know Ping

472
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:22,720
risked everything
for this game?

473
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,599
Risked what?

474
00:22:24,759 --> 00:22:26,359
He just hurt one leg.

475
00:22:26,359 --> 00:22:27,440
He's still alive

476
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:28,200
right here, isn't he?

477
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:30,160
If you want to join the provincial team,

478
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:31,119
go find the coach yourselves.

479
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:32,880
Anyway, Wu has

480
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:34,079
no interest in the provincial team.

481
00:22:34,279 --> 00:22:34,759
What do you mean?
You want to fight, right?

482
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,880
I don't want to fight.

483
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,519
I'm just telling the truth. What?

484
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,000
Can't I tell the truth?

485
00:22:40,079 --> 00:22:41,720
It's an injured leg, not a crippled one.

486
00:22:42,279 --> 00:22:43,279
Stop causing trouble, okay?

487
00:22:43,359 --> 00:22:43,880
No, you...

488
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:45,079
Is hitting people all you know?

489
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:46,200
Who are you pushing?

490
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:47,599
Don't make me hit you.

491
00:22:48,119 --> 00:22:49,079
Everyone, say less.

492
00:22:49,839 --> 00:22:51,359
My buddy speaks harshly.

493
00:22:51,759 --> 00:22:52,440
Sorry about that.

494
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:54,519
I'll drink to you.

495
00:22:55,359 --> 00:22:55,960
Wait.

496
00:22:58,839 --> 00:22:59,640
Use this.

497
00:23:02,519 --> 00:23:03,000
Exactly.

498
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,160
Why so arrogant?
You're using this

499
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:05,519
to toast Ping?

500
00:23:05,519 --> 00:23:06,759
Are you taking my kindness for weakness?

501
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:07,640
What do you mean?
Who are you pushing?

502
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,119
What do you mean?
I don't mean anything.

503
00:23:10,039 --> 00:23:10,440
Touch me again.
Try touching me again.

504
00:23:11,359 --> 00:23:12,039
If you dare hit me,
I'll drop right here

505
00:23:12,759 --> 00:23:13,799
and make you pay for it.

506
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:14,519
Hit me.

507
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:15,920
Right, right, Cao Ping.

508
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:17,400
The provincial team

509
00:23:17,680 --> 00:23:19,079
doesn't take cripples, does it?

510
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:20,440
Say that again.

511
00:23:36,079 --> 00:23:36,720
Hit me.

512
00:23:37,519 --> 00:23:38,039
Kyle.

513
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:00,359
Cao Ping.

514
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:02,000
I have absolutely no interest

515
00:24:02,599 --> 00:24:03,400
in the provincial team.

516
00:24:19,759 --> 00:24:20,559
Xing Wu.

517
00:24:25,079 --> 00:24:25,759
Wu.

518
00:24:30,359 --> 00:24:31,000
Wu.

519
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:33,160
Call 120 now.

520
00:24:33,759 --> 00:24:34,559
Boss.

521
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,279
Call an ambulance.

522
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:04,640
In a moment of rage,

523
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:07,240
Cao Ping slashed my back.

524
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:08,960
He got two years.

525
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:17,359
If

526
00:25:18,279 --> 00:25:19,319
that hadn't happened,

527
00:25:21,279 --> 00:25:22,880
would you have applied to be a pilot?

528
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,119
Maybe this is fate.

529
00:25:31,839 --> 00:25:32,839
I used to think

530
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,039
I was so close to my dream.

531
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:39,759
Take off your shirt.

532
00:25:50,359 --> 00:25:51,000
Turn around.

533
00:26:04,519 --> 00:26:05,319
Student Xing Wu,

534
00:26:08,799 --> 00:26:09,599
please step outside first.

535
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:22,160
I once heard someone say

536
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:24,799
that days crushed by pain

537
00:26:25,599 --> 00:26:26,559
are like

538
00:26:27,240 --> 00:26:29,240
mud left after the tide goes out.

539
00:26:29,599 --> 00:26:30,519
They may look miserable,

540
00:26:30,799 --> 00:26:31,400
but

541
00:26:31,759 --> 00:26:33,440
when the sun rises,

542
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:35,720
shell fragments appear

543
00:26:36,039 --> 00:26:37,079
and reflect dazzling colors.

544
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:39,160
Those colors

545
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:41,680
will become marks of life

546
00:26:42,559 --> 00:26:43,680
that belong only to you.

547
00:26:49,960 --> 00:26:50,920
Each of us

548
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:52,839
has a life path we want to pursue.

549
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:54,680
Take me, for example.

550
00:26:55,519 --> 00:26:57,119
I thought that by now

551
00:26:57,240 --> 00:26:58,359
I'd be studying abroad.

552
00:26:58,599 --> 00:26:59,319
But look where I am.

553
00:27:03,079 --> 00:27:04,440
But I never blame

554
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:06,680
fate for putting me here,

555
00:27:07,440 --> 00:27:08,680
for letting me live

556
00:27:09,359 --> 00:27:10,519
another kind of life in Zhazhating.

557
00:27:13,039 --> 00:27:14,319
On the contrary, I'm grateful.

558
00:27:16,119 --> 00:27:17,880
Because every second here

559
00:27:20,240 --> 00:27:22,119
makes my youth all the more dazzling.

560
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:51,519
Well...

561
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,240
It's late.

562
00:27:53,759 --> 00:27:54,599
Go back early.

563
00:28:03,039 --> 00:28:03,880
Good luck

564
00:28:05,559 --> 00:28:06,200
on tomorrow's test.

565
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:09,079
Don't worry.

566
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,279
I'm aiming to win.

567
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:15,680
Here.

568
00:28:37,559 --> 00:28:38,000
Over there.
Okay.

569
00:28:50,319 --> 00:28:51,079
These past few days,

570
00:28:51,079 --> 00:28:52,319
she seems to eat

571
00:28:53,319 --> 00:28:54,720
and study alone.

572
00:28:55,119 --> 00:28:56,079
Look at her act.

573
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:59,240
What a fake good girl.

574
00:28:59,559 --> 00:29:00,960
If she still doesn't get picked,

575
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,640
I'd be embarrassed for her.

576
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:06,559
At least she's working hard.

577
00:29:06,799 --> 00:29:07,440
Good for her.

578
00:29:08,519 --> 00:29:09,920
Even working hard, she can't beat Qing Ye.

579
00:29:10,039 --> 00:29:10,640
Working hard?
You eat first.

580
00:29:11,279 --> 00:29:11,960
I'll go over.
We'll see.

581
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:15,240
I can't stand people like her.

582
00:29:23,279 --> 00:29:24,079
Why are you glaring at us?

583
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:29,519
What?

584
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:30,720
Eat.

585
00:29:32,319 --> 00:29:33,680
If you don't eat now, it'll get cold.

586
00:29:35,039 --> 00:29:35,839
None of your business.

587
00:29:37,599 --> 00:29:39,759
You don't look well.

588
00:29:40,279 --> 00:29:41,039
Are you okay?

589
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,319
Mind your own business.

590
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:56,519
Okay. Begin answering now.

591
00:31:12,119 --> 00:31:12,799
Sir! Sir!

592
00:31:13,279 --> 00:31:14,119
Cao Fan fainted.

593
00:31:15,119 --> 00:31:15,559
Cao Fan.
What's wrong?

594
00:31:16,519 --> 00:31:16,960
Cao Fan.
Cao Fan.

595
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:18,319
How are you?

596
00:31:37,759 --> 00:31:38,440
Hello? What happened?

597
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:39,920
Brother Ping, bad news.
Bad news.

598
00:31:40,519 --> 00:31:41,480
Didn't you ask me
to have someone watch your sister?

599
00:31:42,519 --> 00:31:44,039
She's out cold at the county hospital.

600
00:31:44,319 --> 00:31:45,119
It doesn't look good.

601
00:31:45,519 --> 00:31:47,160
Xing Wu and his sister

602
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:47,720
brought her in.
My guess is

603
00:31:48,839 --> 00:31:50,000
it has something to do with them.

604
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:52,960
Doctor.

605
00:31:54,039 --> 00:31:55,519
How is this child?

606
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:57,440
38.9 degrees.

607
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:58,559
That's a high fever.

608
00:31:58,920 --> 00:31:59,880
We also ran blood tests just now.

609
00:32:00,279 --> 00:32:01,000
Low blood sugar.

610
00:32:01,079 --> 00:32:02,839
She's a little malnourished too.

611
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,119
And the nosebleed?

612
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:05,279
Her nasal membrane is too dry.

613
00:32:05,559 --> 00:32:07,079
Looks like she's been staying up late

614
00:32:07,319 --> 00:32:08,119
and not resting well.

615
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:09,200
Doctor,

616
00:32:09,319 --> 00:32:10,599
when will she wake up?

617
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:12,400
From the look of it,
she's still very weak.

618
00:32:13,599 --> 00:32:14,160
Of course,

619
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,599
it's nothing too serious.

620
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:17,200
Let her rest properly first.

621
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:18,519
Call me if anything comes up.

622
00:32:18,759 --> 00:32:19,160
Okay.

623
00:32:19,519 --> 00:32:20,200
Thank you, doctor.

624
00:32:23,519 --> 00:32:24,200
Mr. Zhu.

625
00:32:24,640 --> 00:32:25,720
Why don't you go back to school first?

626
00:32:26,079 --> 00:32:27,160
We'll stay here with her.

627
00:32:28,559 --> 00:32:29,160
All right.

628
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:30,880
I'll come after evening study

629
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:31,839
to take over from you.

630
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:32,799
Okay.
Thank you, Xing Wu.

631
00:32:38,519 --> 00:32:39,200
Actually,

632
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,680
before the exam, I already noticed

633
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,880
something was wrong with her.

634
00:32:42,359 --> 00:32:44,000
I should've told the teacher sooner.

635
00:32:45,519 --> 00:32:46,519
Don't overthink it.

636
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:47,920
The doctor just said

637
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:49,079
it's nothing serious.

638
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,279
Don't worry.

639
00:32:52,599 --> 00:32:53,640
I'll go buy you something to eat.

640
00:34:37,239 --> 00:34:37,960
You're awake.

641
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:40,800
How do you feel? Better?

642
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:52,039
I have a thermos here.

643
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:53,360
Weren't you looking for one earlier?

644
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:54,119
Use this for now.

645
00:34:54,719 --> 00:34:55,320
Thank you.

646
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:56,519
The water room is over there.

647
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:58,199
I can go myself.
Okay.

648
00:35:02,639 --> 00:35:03,639
I know you blame me.

649
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:08,280
I failed as your brother.

650
00:35:10,639 --> 00:35:11,960
No wonder you don't want to talk to me.

651
00:35:20,559 --> 00:35:21,679
If anyone at school bullies you,

652
00:35:21,679 --> 00:35:22,440
remember to tell me.

653
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:25,920
Then what?

654
00:35:32,199 --> 00:35:33,280
Will you hit people again

655
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,159
like before?

656
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:36,000
Too many people bully me.

657
00:35:36,119 --> 00:35:37,079
Can you fight them all?

658
00:35:43,639 --> 00:35:44,320
Just go.

659
00:35:44,840 --> 00:35:45,719
I can't sleep if you don't leave.

660
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:51,679
Take care of yourself.

661
00:36:29,119 --> 00:36:30,639
Xing Wu and his sister

662
00:36:30,679 --> 00:36:31,239
brought her in.
My guess is

663
00:36:32,159 --> 00:36:33,360
it has something to do with them.

664
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:35,360
Too many people bully me.

665
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:36,400
Can you fight them all?

666
00:37:01,559 --> 00:37:02,400
Where do you think you're going?

667
00:37:05,599 --> 00:37:06,880
You're Cao Fan's brother,

668
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:07,599
Cao Ping, right?

669
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:09,920
I think you've misunderstood.

670
00:37:10,559 --> 00:37:11,880
Cao Fan and I aren't enemies.

671
00:37:12,079 --> 00:37:12,840
You don't need to explain.

672
00:37:14,119 --> 00:37:14,840
My sister

673
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:16,119
ended up like this today

674
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,800
because of you two siblings.

675
00:37:19,519 --> 00:37:20,719
You really misunderstood.

676
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,119
This is a hospital.

677
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,000
People will come any minute.

678
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:27,360
I think you'd better calm down.

679
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:40,760
You think I'm scared?

680
00:37:46,199 --> 00:37:46,920
Your sister fainting

681
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,199
really wasn't caused by me.

682
00:37:50,159 --> 00:37:51,519
We were taking the exam.

683
00:37:51,760 --> 00:37:52,559
Then she suddenly
started sweating a lot

684
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,840
and fainted.

685
00:38:05,719 --> 00:38:07,159
Your fried rice, young man.

686
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:09,079
Let go.

687
00:38:09,519 --> 00:38:10,599
Let go. Who are you calling?

688
00:38:20,119 --> 00:38:20,599
Don't be afraid.
I'm here.

689
00:38:30,159 --> 00:38:30,880
Go back first.

690
00:38:31,719 --> 00:38:32,519
I'll talk to him.

691
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:34,639
No, but...

692
00:38:35,639 --> 00:38:36,280
Don't worry.

693
00:38:37,639 --> 00:38:38,400
I know what I'm doing.

694
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:40,400
Go back.

695
00:38:41,199 --> 00:38:41,719
Okay.

696
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,639
I'll go back first.

697
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:45,840
If you don't come back
in ten minutes,

698
00:38:48,239 --> 00:38:49,119
I'll call the police.

699
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:52,679
Go on.

700
00:39:14,199 --> 00:39:15,800
I told you not to touch my people.

701
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:18,559
Pretty strong.

702
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:21,239
What if I insist?

703
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:23,199
What will you do?

704
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,039
Simple.

705
00:39:26,519 --> 00:39:27,840
I want you, like me,

706
00:39:28,679 --> 00:39:29,480
abandoned by everyone.

707
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:31,159
Then I'll be satisfied.

708
00:39:33,079 --> 00:39:34,119
Then come at me.

709
00:39:47,119 --> 00:39:47,840
In three days,

710
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,079
we settle this once and for all.

711
00:39:53,360 --> 00:39:53,920
Fine.

712
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:14,159
Sit here for now.

713
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:16,320
Boss.

714
00:40:17,239 --> 00:40:18,239
Two more fried rice.

715
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:19,280
No scallions, less spicy.
Sure.

716
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:20,880
And the one from earlier.
I'll pay for that too.

717
00:40:21,599 --> 00:40:21,960
Okay.
Add an egg to one.

718
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:23,960
Sure, sure.

719
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:30,519
Are you hurt?

720
00:40:31,519 --> 00:40:32,159
No.

721
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:43,079
Did that scare you?

722
00:40:49,159 --> 00:40:50,960
It's my fault. I dragged you into this.

723
00:40:53,679 --> 00:40:54,920
Actually, I didn't lose out either.

724
00:40:58,239 --> 00:40:59,320
How did your talk go?

725
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:02,840
Nothing happened. It went fine.

726
00:41:04,239 --> 00:41:05,239
Anyway, don't worry.

727
00:41:05,719 --> 00:41:06,559
I'll handle everything.

728
00:42:15,559 --> 00:42:16,519
Why did you come here to find me?

729
00:42:16,719 --> 00:42:17,920
I came to bring you food.

730
00:42:18,119 --> 00:42:19,239
What good food did you make me?

731
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:22,239
Dumplings, braised pork,

732
00:42:22,519 --> 00:42:23,320
and other dishes.
All your favorites.

733
00:42:24,679 --> 00:42:25,719
Then wait for me a bit.

734
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:29,320
Wait.
Brother.

735
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:31,119
Why are you staring at me like that?

736
00:42:31,119 --> 00:42:31,760
Brother.

737
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:32,760
I saw a watch recently.

738
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:34,679
It looks really nice.

739
00:42:34,679 --> 00:42:35,360
A watch?

740
00:42:36,199 --> 00:42:36,840
Why do you need a watch?

741
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,400
I just...

742
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,119
All right, show me.

743
00:42:40,519 --> 00:42:41,239
Come on, open it.
This one.

744
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:44,360
It is pretty nice.

745
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:46,239
Okay.

746
00:42:49,599 --> 00:42:50,039
After I finish the game,

747
00:42:50,239 --> 00:42:51,599
I'll buy it for you

748
00:42:51,599 --> 00:42:52,440
with the prize money.

749
00:43:15,199 --> 00:43:16,079
You're about to be discharged.

750
00:43:17,199 --> 00:43:17,679
Don't act like
you know me so well.

751
00:43:19,519 --> 00:43:20,320
Consider yesterday my debt to you.

752
00:43:20,519 --> 00:43:21,559
I'll find a chance to repay it.

753
00:43:22,119 --> 00:43:23,320
How about you owe me one more,

754
00:43:23,639 --> 00:43:24,599
then pay me back big?

755
00:43:26,639 --> 00:43:27,440
What do you mean?

756
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:29,960
You should go to the winter camp.

757
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:32,199
You want to give me your spot?

758
00:43:34,519 --> 00:43:35,719
But I have one condition.

759
00:43:36,519 --> 00:43:37,719
Help your brother and Xing Wu reconcile.
